    {
        "content": "<p>Here's a screenshot of the issue:</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/4Uowk__8L95_nP3h0qNoyaf5/Screenshot-2024-08-12-at-7.27.03AM.png\">Screenshot-2024-08-12-at-7.27.03AM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/4Uowk__8L95_nP3h0qNoyaf5/Screenshot-2024-08-12-at-7.27.03AM.png\" title=\"Screenshot-2024-08-12-at-7.27.03AM.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"3644x2360\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/4Uowk__8L95_nP3h0qNoyaf5/Screenshot-2024-08-12-at-7.27.03AM.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
